00:00:00,040 --> 00:00:14,740
( Watch on Kissasia.vip )

1
00:01:05,760 --> 00:01:08,192
=No Doubt In Us=
(Adapted from the Manman comic No Doubt in Us)

2
00:01:08,320 --> 00:01:11,232
=Episode 24=

3
00:01:11,400 --> 00:01:12,879
Prince Ning spreads lies

4
00:01:13,200 --> 00:01:14,239
to usurp the throne!

5
00:01:14,920 --> 00:01:15,840
Seize him!

6
00:02:16,639 --> 00:02:18,840
Jinyun, leave our uncle to me.

7
00:02:19,199 --> 00:02:20,919
Time to settle our scores.

8
00:02:35,120 --> 00:02:37,599
Xiao Jinyun, I'm your opponent.

9
00:02:38,240 --> 00:02:40,360
You imprisoned Xu Yu in the palace.

10
00:02:40,840 --> 00:02:42,120
You caused her death.

11
00:02:43,240 --> 00:02:45,039
Today, I will avenge her.

12
00:03:12,599 --> 00:03:14,680
Xu Yu is here, at your service!

13
00:03:20,000 --> 00:03:20,879
No one noticed, right?

14
00:03:21,439 --> 00:03:22,240
No one noticed.

15
00:03:22,719 --> 00:03:23,560
Not even His Majesty.

16
00:03:24,080 --> 00:03:24,800
But...

17
00:03:26,000 --> 00:03:27,719
Why keep it from even His Majesty?

18
00:03:28,400 --> 00:03:29,360
I didn't.

19
00:03:30,080 --> 00:03:31,080
I left him a letter.

20
00:03:31,879 --> 00:03:33,439
The Grand Preceptor would hint to him.

21
00:03:34,599 --> 00:03:37,879
(Xiao Jinyun, I finally tricked you.)

22
00:03:38,360 --> 00:03:39,840
(I'm not going to die.)

23
00:03:40,280 --> 00:03:42,800
(Jiang Tang got the herbs Jinming found)

24
00:03:42,800 --> 00:03:44,360
(and developed the antidote first.)

25
00:03:44,759 --> 00:03:47,759
(Now, the situation
in the palace is a deadlock.)

26
00:03:48,360 --> 00:03:50,319
(One of us must break it.)

27
00:03:50,639 --> 00:03:53,440
(I am the member of Xu family
and your wife.)

28
00:03:53,919 --> 00:03:55,159
(Whether it's the empire,)

29
00:03:55,159 --> 00:03:56,000
(the Emperor,)

30
00:03:56,360 --> 00:03:57,560
(or my husband,)

31
00:03:57,680 --> 00:03:59,120
(it is my duty to save them all.)

32
00:03:59,599 --> 00:04:01,199
(That's why I staged this act)

33
00:04:01,199 --> 00:04:02,199
(to deceive everyone)

34
00:04:02,280 --> 00:04:04,439
(and leave Chen and join the Xu army.)

35
00:04:04,800 --> 00:04:07,039
(Now, let Prince Ning
and his cohorts come out)

36
00:04:07,039 --> 00:04:08,159
(and crush them at a time.)

37
00:04:11,439 --> 00:04:11,960
Your Majesty.

38
00:04:12,599 --> 00:04:13,919
Those two are gone.

39
00:04:14,639 --> 00:04:15,680
How's it going?

40
00:04:16,120 --> 00:04:18,399
Her Majesty and Huna
will follow your orders

41
00:04:18,759 --> 00:04:20,360
and arrive on the day of the rite.

42
00:04:23,560 --> 00:04:27,319
You lowlifes dare dream
of shaking Chen Empire?

43
00:04:27,879 --> 00:04:28,519
Soldiers!

44
00:04:29,600 --> 00:04:30,759
Seize the traitors!

45
00:04:31,000 --> 00:04:32,199
Kill the rebels!

46
00:04:48,800 --> 00:04:49,300
Xu Yu.

47
00:04:50,240 --> 00:04:50,879
You're back.

48
00:04:58,920 --> 00:04:59,959
I was careless.

49
00:04:59,959 --> 00:05:01,480
You faked your death.

50
00:05:01,879 --> 00:05:03,839
With villains like you still at large,

51
00:05:03,839 --> 00:05:05,279
how could I possibly die?

52
00:05:05,839 --> 00:05:07,120
His Majesty set this trap

53
00:05:07,560 --> 00:05:10,439
just to expose
your vicious ambition to the world.

54
00:05:13,040 --> 00:05:13,680
Xiao Jinyun.

55
00:05:14,360 --> 00:05:16,120
I don't believe in Heaven's pity.

56
00:05:16,319 --> 00:05:19,519
I only believe in our unwavering love.

57
00:05:20,000 --> 00:05:22,920
My husband will be protected by me.

58
00:05:26,560 --> 00:05:29,279
You infected the city for selfish gain!

59
00:05:29,720 --> 00:05:30,680
Thanks to the antidote,

60
00:05:30,680 --> 00:05:31,839
the people are safe.

61
00:05:32,279 --> 00:05:33,240
My two brothers

62
00:05:33,600 --> 00:05:36,199
have blocked your remaining mercenaries
outside the walls.

63
00:05:36,519 --> 00:05:39,079
Prince Ning, if you don't surrender now.

64
00:05:39,639 --> 00:05:43,360
I will execute you immediately
for those innocent lives.

65
00:05:43,800 --> 00:05:45,000
A sacrifice to the people.

66
00:05:49,000 --> 00:05:50,279
Don't celebrate too soon.

67
00:05:50,680 --> 00:05:53,856
The armies of the Prince of Luoyang
and Prince of Zhennan will arrive today.

68
00:05:54,000 --> 00:05:56,279
You still can't hold the capital.

69
00:05:57,120 --> 00:05:57,879
Is that so?

70
00:06:24,399 --> 00:06:26,240
Marshal Xu's victory report!

71
00:06:26,240 --> 00:06:28,279
Working with Dada,

72
00:06:28,279 --> 00:06:29,639
they crushed the barbarians.

73
00:06:29,839 --> 00:06:33,279
The Prince of Luoyang and the Prince
of Zhennan returned to their domains.

74
00:06:33,720 --> 00:06:34,680
How can this be?

75
00:06:35,040 --> 00:06:36,959
The reason I stand here today

76
00:06:36,959 --> 00:06:39,720
is not just the Xu army
guarding our empire,

77
00:06:40,120 --> 00:06:42,360
but countless soldiers
who yearn for peace

78
00:06:42,360 --> 00:06:43,639
and fear no death,

79
00:06:44,240 --> 00:06:47,879
and our people who cherish every day
even in the simplest of lives.

80
00:06:48,480 --> 00:06:52,240
Isn't a ruler yearning for
the people's peace and prosperity

81
00:06:52,480 --> 00:06:53,800
and a world without war?

82
00:06:54,560 --> 00:06:56,759
So, you will lose.

83
00:06:57,040 --> 00:06:57,879
Xiao Jinyun!

84
00:06:59,000 --> 00:07:01,800
10 years ago, I didn't seek
power against you.

85
00:07:01,920 --> 00:07:05,920
Your father killed
my wife's family on false charges.

86
00:07:06,439 --> 00:07:08,040
I begged him desperately,

87
00:07:08,399 --> 00:07:10,560
but he still killed them.

88
00:07:11,279 --> 00:07:14,399
Now, taking his son's life is only fair!

89
00:07:14,680 --> 00:07:16,439
If anyone is wrong, it's you!

90
00:07:16,720 --> 00:07:18,439
You wronged me first!

91
00:07:18,439 --> 00:07:19,160
Absurd!

92
00:07:20,720 --> 00:07:23,920
You and they clearly
fought for the throne.

93
00:07:24,720 --> 00:07:25,759
Now, things happened,

94
00:07:25,759 --> 00:07:27,199
and you wash your hands clean.

95
00:07:29,079 --> 00:07:31,199
Pitiable is Princess Ning's family.

96
00:07:32,040 --> 00:07:34,040
Each was loyal and righteous.

97
00:07:34,279 --> 00:07:35,720
Not one named you, even in death.

98
00:07:36,120 --> 00:07:38,720
But they faced extermination.

99
00:07:39,680 --> 00:07:42,079
Your ambition killed them!

100
00:07:44,279 --> 00:07:47,439
Y-You're twisting the truth!

101
00:07:48,279 --> 00:07:50,959
Your letter of repentance
to my father is still here.

102
00:07:51,560 --> 00:07:55,079
It clearly states you were coerced
by treacherous individuals

103
00:07:55,319 --> 00:07:56,480
and were completely unaware.

104
00:07:57,600 --> 00:08:01,120
Doesn't your conscience
trouble you even now?

105
00:08:34,200 --> 00:08:35,120
Xiao Jinle!

106
00:08:35,679 --> 00:08:37,000
Insane. You killed your father.

107
00:08:37,320 --> 00:08:38,360
And now, you're laughing?

108
00:08:38,840 --> 00:08:40,159
I got my revenge right this time.

109
00:08:40,159 --> 00:08:41,600
Shouldn't I be laughing?

110
00:08:43,120 --> 00:08:43,799
Xu Yu.

111
00:08:44,559 --> 00:08:46,000
Back then, you saved me.

112
00:08:46,279 --> 00:08:48,840
I vowed to rescue you
from this gilded cage of a palace.

113
00:08:49,440 --> 00:08:51,000
I thought you were dead,

114
00:08:52,000 --> 00:08:54,320
so I planted explosives here.

115
00:08:55,120 --> 00:08:57,559
Today, no matter who sits on the throne,

116
00:08:57,960 --> 00:09:00,240
everyone here must die!

117
00:09:00,240 --> 00:09:01,919
They will all join you in death!

118
00:09:02,519 --> 00:09:04,200
But now, you're alive.

119
00:09:04,960 --> 00:09:07,440
We shall go to die together!

120
00:09:08,559 --> 00:09:09,960
If we cannot live together,

121
00:09:10,159 --> 00:09:11,840
we shall die together.

122
00:09:12,200 --> 00:09:13,120
You're wrong.

123
00:09:14,240 --> 00:09:15,879
No one will die today,

124
00:09:16,799 --> 00:09:18,000
except you all.

125
00:09:20,399 --> 00:09:21,039
Your Majesty,

126
00:09:21,639 --> 00:09:23,240
all explosives here have been removed.

127
00:09:23,679 --> 00:09:24,399
All is safe.

128
00:09:26,679 --> 00:09:28,440
Another traitor.

129
00:09:28,919 --> 00:09:29,919
Xiao Jinyun!

130
00:09:30,679 --> 00:09:32,919
Do you think this was my only plan?

131
00:09:39,799 --> 00:09:42,600
(As long as I kill
the Grand Preceptor of Chen,)

132
00:09:43,360 --> 00:09:46,600
(the entire palace
will fall under my sorcery.)

133
00:09:57,279 --> 00:09:58,360
Evil sorcery.

134
00:09:59,279 --> 00:10:00,639
Your death won't be mourned.

135
00:10:07,039 --> 00:10:08,320
Don't dirty

136
00:10:09,519 --> 00:10:10,759
my place.

137
00:10:11,759 --> 00:10:13,320
You small fry!

138
00:10:13,519 --> 00:10:15,440
Her Majesty set the trap long ago,

139
00:10:15,919 --> 00:10:17,279
just waiting

140
00:10:17,279 --> 00:10:18,080
to catch you all!

141
00:10:19,200 --> 00:10:20,039
Your Highness,

142
00:10:20,320 --> 00:10:22,159
did we truly defend
Ci'an Palace on our own?

143
00:10:22,440 --> 00:10:23,559
Of course!

144
00:10:23,559 --> 00:10:26,080
We have trained in martial arts!

145
00:10:26,080 --> 00:10:27,000
We are formidable!

146
00:10:29,159 --> 00:10:30,039
Your Majesty,

147
00:10:31,080 --> 00:10:33,279
I have fulfilled my duty.

148
00:10:34,039 --> 00:10:35,440
I held the harem for you.

149
00:10:36,279 --> 00:10:39,320
If you think you've sent men
to attack Ci'an Palace

150
00:10:39,759 --> 00:10:41,679
and that the women
of the harem are all weak,

151
00:10:41,919 --> 00:10:43,120
you are wrong again!

152
00:10:43,440 --> 00:10:46,919
And you'll pay the price
for your actions!

153
00:11:26,399 --> 00:11:29,799
His Majesty has decreed
to restore the consorts' freedom.

154
00:11:30,159 --> 00:11:33,159
They will be returned
to their families as imperial sisters,

155
00:11:34,440 --> 00:11:37,159
and they may marry as they wish.

156
00:11:38,679 --> 00:11:41,279
Their Majesties
will see them wed with princess rites.

157
00:11:42,080 --> 00:11:43,480
With such favorable terms,

158
00:11:44,840 --> 00:11:45,840
why aren't you leaving?

159
00:11:46,200 --> 00:11:47,480
You're no different.

160
00:11:47,639 --> 00:11:48,559
You don't return.

161
00:11:49,200 --> 00:11:49,720
What?

162
00:11:50,480 --> 00:11:52,279
Still hoping His Majesty will favor you?

163
00:11:53,080 --> 00:11:55,679
I am now a Female Secretary
personally appointed by His Majesty!

164
00:11:56,679 --> 00:11:58,519
Her Majesty secured this for me.

165
00:11:59,799 --> 00:12:02,679
I now manage palace affairs.

166
00:12:02,960 --> 00:12:06,320
In the future, I will assist Her Majesty
in selecting female officials.

167
00:12:06,960 --> 00:12:11,080
From now on, female officials
in Chen can also serve in government.

168
00:12:12,799 --> 00:12:15,000
Men? Who needs them?

169
00:12:16,200 --> 00:12:18,440
My father will need me
to bring honor to our family soon!

170
00:12:18,639 --> 00:12:19,919
Dear,

171
00:12:20,320 --> 00:12:22,559
how about giving me
a palace official position?

172
00:12:22,960 --> 00:12:25,720
How about we build our careers together?

173
00:12:26,919 --> 00:12:27,759
That's it!

174
00:12:31,559 --> 00:12:32,559
The other feudal lords

175
00:12:33,320 --> 00:12:35,799
did not object to confiscating
Prince Ning's estate.

176
00:12:36,720 --> 00:12:40,240
The Chen Empire
now enjoys internal stability.

177
00:12:42,080 --> 00:12:43,200
The northwest is pacified.

178
00:12:43,440 --> 00:12:45,559
Huna is spreading
your majesty far and wide

179
00:12:45,559 --> 00:12:46,399
to cow the tribes.

180
00:12:46,919 --> 00:12:48,919
Now, the borders are secure.

181
00:12:51,360 --> 00:12:52,080
Xu Yu.

182
00:12:52,960 --> 00:12:54,120
We met as kids.

183
00:12:54,600 --> 00:12:56,639
If I hadn't kept my distance back then

184
00:12:56,799 --> 00:12:58,360
and instead remained close with you,

185
00:13:00,000 --> 00:13:01,840
the court wouldn't have stood
for our marriage,

186
00:13:02,240 --> 00:13:03,600
let alone making you the Empress.

187
00:13:05,159 --> 00:13:06,440
What do you mean?

188
00:13:07,039 --> 00:13:07,679
I mean,

189
00:13:08,720 --> 00:13:11,679
if we had always been a loving couple,

190
00:13:12,159 --> 00:13:16,480
the court would have viewed you
and your family as an eyesore.

191
00:13:17,559 --> 00:13:19,519
I did not want that.

192
00:13:23,440 --> 00:13:24,919
Are you saying...

193
00:13:25,120 --> 00:13:26,240
I mean,

194
00:13:26,799 --> 00:13:29,159
I might have started
paying attention to you in secret

195
00:13:30,360 --> 00:13:31,679
when I first knew you.

196
00:13:33,279 --> 00:13:36,639
Later, when you came to my palace
to see me time and again,

197
00:13:37,440 --> 00:13:38,639
I became even more certain

198
00:13:40,759 --> 00:13:41,559
that I liked you.

199
00:13:42,400 --> 00:13:46,963
♪Brewing a pot of bygone years♪

200
00:13:47,159 --> 00:13:47,840
Xu Yu,

201
00:13:49,399 --> 00:13:50,720
I treated you badly before.

202
00:13:53,440 --> 00:13:55,759
I wish to spend this life making amends

203
00:13:56,440 --> 00:13:57,799
and grow old together with you.

204
00:13:59,456 --> 00:14:04,720
♪If not for letting go, how could I
bear to shatter this dream♪

205
00:14:05,088 --> 00:14:10,765
♪Returning to drift
through the mortal world♪

206
00:14:11,104 --> 00:14:13,120
♪Like her, like me, like you♪

207
00:14:13,312 --> 00:14:17,056
♪Hairpins carved
with endless sighs and regrets♪

208
00:14:17,632 --> 00:14:22,304
♪Fate laid bare my deepest thoughts♪

209
00:14:22,848 --> 00:14:24,608
♪Like vows, like remorse, like love♪

210
00:14:24,928 --> 00:14:28,440
♪Loving, hurting,
and regretting our late meeting♪

211
00:14:28,440 --> 00:14:29,320
I wish

212
00:14:31,159 --> 00:14:32,399
to grow old with you too.

213
00:14:34,432 --> 00:14:36,512
♪Like her, like me, like you♪

214
00:14:36,512 --> 00:14:40,832
♪All who believed love would never fade♪

215
00:14:40,832 --> 00:14:44,960
♪The wind scatters countless sorrows♪

216
00:14:44,960 --> 00:14:46,200
With a wife like you,

217
00:14:48,519 --> 00:14:50,039
how could my empire not be secure?

218
00:14:52,120 --> 00:14:57,792
♪No one ferries me
across this sea of pain♪

219
00:14:57,792 --> 00:15:03,067
♪The same joys and sorrows
can't be relived♪

220
00:15:27,152 --> 00:15:32,159
♪If not for letting go, how could I
bear to shatter this dream♪

221
00:15:32,159 --> 00:15:33,639
Celebrating six years

222
00:15:33,879 --> 00:15:35,399
of the imperial marriage.

223
00:15:35,919 --> 00:15:40,080
May your bond stay eternal,

224
00:15:40,440 --> 00:15:43,320
and may the Chen Empire flourish

225
00:15:43,480 --> 00:15:45,679
for all ages!

226
00:15:46,480 --> 00:15:48,159
- Flourish
- Flourish

227
00:15:48,440 --> 00:15:50,360
- for all ages!
- for all ages!

228
00:15:50,759 --> 00:15:51,600
Everyone,

229
00:15:53,000 --> 00:15:53,720
rise.

230
00:15:54,320 --> 00:15:55,840
- Thank you.
- Thank you.

231
00:15:56,608 --> 00:16:01,519
♪Tell me, after all this entanglement,
who regrets it more♪

232
00:16:01,519 --> 00:16:02,840
Bound as husband and wife.

233
00:16:04,679 --> 00:16:05,879
No doubt in us.

234
00:16:08,736 --> 00:16:13,824
♪The wind scatters countless sorrows♪

235
00:16:13,824 --> 00:16:15,584
♪Like a song, like a dream, like a play♪

236
00:16:15,584 --> 00:16:17,542
(The end)

237
00:16:32,896 --> 00:16:38,080
♪Parting clouds
to pluck the waxing moon♪

238
00:16:38,816 --> 00:16:43,379
♪Brewing a pot of bygone years♪

239
00:16:44,704 --> 00:16:50,119
♪Chill flame, window shade,
console my grieving soul♪

240
00:16:50,688 --> 00:16:55,232
♪Drunk through lifetimes
with no dreams returned♪

241
00:16:55,872 --> 00:17:01,136
♪If not for letting go, how could I
bear to shatter this dream♪

242
00:17:01,504 --> 00:17:07,181
♪Returning to drift
through the mortal world♪

243
00:17:07,520 --> 00:17:09,536
♪Like her, like me, like you♪

244
00:17:09,728 --> 00:17:13,472
♪Hairpins carved
with endless sighs and regrets♪

245
00:17:14,048 --> 00:17:18,720
♪Fate laid bare my deepest thoughts♪

246
00:17:19,264 --> 00:17:21,024
♪Like vows, like remorse, like love♪

247
00:17:21,344 --> 00:17:24,960
♪Loving, hurting,
and regretting our late meeting♪

248
